data.description: Welcome Home to Tidewater Preserve, a luxury boating community in the heart of Bradenton. This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home has an ASSUMABLE VA MORTGAGE available at 2.25% to a qualifying Veteran and is perfect for entertaining or escaping it all. Upon entering, you are enchantingly lured toward the crystal blue waters of the private heated pool and spa. Fountains cascade down into the sparkling blue saltwater capable pool. Complete with a retractable Sunbrella awning for shade on a warm day. A handsome outdoor kitchen evokes thoughts and scents of afternoon barbecues. A grand open floor plan invites you indoors to view expansive rooms adorned with tray ceilings, engineered hardwood floors and granite countertops. Pour yourself a glass of wine on a stormy night and rest easy, knowing that you are safe and sound behind hurricane impact windows and doors. Soak your cares away in the garden tub before drifting off to sleep in this stately primary bedroom. When you awaken from a long night of slumber, you will have absolutely no excuse for boredom! In this maintenance free community, you will find three refreshing pools, two clubhouses, a billiards room, two fitness centers, three lighted Har-Tru® hydro tennis courts, a playground, dog park, a marina with annual slip rentals and boat lift, as well as a kayak launch with rentable kayak storage. Or... you can quiet your mind in the nature park and follow a winding trail that leads you to where the water kisses the sky at the Manatee River Overlook. Tidewater Preserve is just 15 miles to the award-winning, powdery soft beaches of Anna Maria Island. Life is so short. You deserve to live this lifestyle. Come and fall in love with this home and its community today!
